[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
Headroom includes an rc.d script for proxy mode.

To enable it:

sysrc headroom_enable=YES
sysrc headroom_env="OPENAI_API_KEY=your-key"
service headroom start

The package installs the lightweight proxy startup dependencies. Some
Headroom proxy features use heavier optional components such as Magika,
ONNX Runtime, Transformers, MCP, and sqlite-vec. Those are not all
available in mports yet, and ONNX Runtime is not currently suitable for
i386 package builds.
EOM
}
]
